          requirements, electives, and focal areas — letting you shape your education around the career you want.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    {# ── BSc STREAMS ── #}
    <section class="cs-ug-programmes">
      <h2 class="cs-section-label cs-section-label--center">BSc Computer Science Streams</h2>
      <p class="cs-ug-programmes__lead">Five focal areas within our flagship 3-year degree.</p>

