          <span class="cs-ug-prog-card__duration">3 years · BSc</span>
          <p class="cs-ug-prog-card__desc">
            Combines the CS major with Electric &amp; Electronic Engineering modules. Ideal for students interested
            in hardware, system-level programming, and embedded systems.
          </p>
