        <div class="cs-ug-prog-card">
          <div class="cs-ug-prog-card__icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M18 20V10M12 20V4M6 20v-6"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="cs-ug-prog-card__title">Data Science Focus</h3>
          <span class="cs-ug-prog-card__duration">3 years · BSc</span>
          <p class="cs-ug-prog-card__desc">
            Integrates CS with Statistics and Data Science modules. Perfect for aspiring data scientists and analysts
            who want a strong mathematical and computational foundation.
          </p>
          <div class="cs-ug-prog-card__tags">
            <span>Statistics</span>
            <span>Analytics</span>
            <span>ML</span>
