          <span class="cs-ug-prog-card__duration">3 years · BSc Double Major</span>
          <p class="cs-ug-prog-card__desc">
            Combines Computer Science with Genetics as a second major. Suited for students interested in
            computational biology, bioinformatics, and genomics.
          </p>
          <div class="cs-ug-prog-card__tags">
            <span>Bioinformatics</span>
            <span>Genomics</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="cs-ug-prog-card">
          <div class="cs-ug-prog-card__icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M2 12h20M12 2a15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4-10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4-10z"/></svg>
